p;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003E(kode)-(digit) Digit menggunakan 3-digit\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003EKode dari yg plg low-end ke yg ekstrim= G\u0026gt;GT\u0026gt;GTS\u0026gt;GTX\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003Edigit 1:\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003E1xx-2xx= tipe kuno, directX 9-10\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003E3xx= khusus laptop, nendukung directX 10.1\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003E4xx-5xx= Fermi class, mendukung directX 11 dan Open GL 4.1-5\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003Edigit 2 (berlaku antar kode)\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003Ex0x-x2x= low-end\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, san-serif; line-height: 16.25px;\"\u003Ex3x-x5x= mainstream\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-c