le=\"font-family: inherit;\"\u003EAturan ini akan berlaku bagi setiap paragraph \u0026lt;p\u0026gt; yang memiliki class=”komentar” saja.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Ch3 style=\"background-color: rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.4); border: 0px; clear: both; color: #222222; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18.66666603088379px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 14px; vertical-align: baseline;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: small;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003EID dapat dipanggil via browser\u003C\/i\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"background-color: rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.4); border: 0px; color: #222222; line-height: 18.66666603088379px; margin-bottom: 22px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit;\"\u003EJika kita ingin memanggil sebuah halaman dan ditambahkan dengan #{namaid} maka akan langsung dibukakan halaman dalam posisi sudah terscroll ke ID tersebut. Contoh silakan saja buka :\u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/bimosaurus.com\/2013\/07\/09\/tutorial-membuat-aplikasi-webchat-dengan-php-mysql-jquery\/#comment\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: #002b71; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"\u003Ehttp:\/\/bimosaurus.com\/2013\/07\/09\/tutorial-membuat-aplikasi-webchat-dengan-php-mysql-jquery\/#comment\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/i\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/christian10ozora.blogspot.com\/feeds\/5190358853517365871\/comments\/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/christian10ozora.blogspot.com\/2014\/02\/perbedaan-id-dan-class-pada-css.html#comment-form","title":"0 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/7914674279276059894\/posts\/default\/5190358853517365871"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/at